flowchart TD
    A[Client submits registration form\nPOST /api/auth/register] --> B[Auth Controller: registerUser]

    B --> C{Required base fields\nuserName, email, password present?}
    C -- No --> E1[400 Bad Request\nPlease fill in all required fields]
    C -- Yes --> D{Role valid?\nsuperAdmin | businessAdministrator | fieldServiceAgent | customer}

    D -- No --> E2[400 Bad Request\nInvalid role specified]
    D -- Yes --> F[Normalize email to lowercase]

    F --> G{Role-specific required fields valid?}
    G -- No --> E3[400 Bad Request\nMissing role-required fields]
    G -- Yes --> H[Check duplicate user\nUser.findOne by email or userName]

    H --> I{User already exists?}
    I -- Yes --> E4[400 Bad Request\nEmail already registered / Username already taken]
    I -- No --> J{Role requires onboarding passkey?\n(businessAdministrator or fieldServiceAgent)}

    J -- Yes --> K[Find active passkey by\ntargetEmail + targetRole]
    K --> L{Passkey record exists?}
    L -- No --> E5[403 Forbidden\nNo active onboarding passkey\nrenewalRequired=true]
    L -- Yes --> M{Passkey expired?}
    M -- Yes --> E6[403 Forbidden\nPasskey expired\nstatus->expired]
    M -- No --> N{Passkey hash matches?}
    N -- No --> E7[401 Unauthorized\nInvalid passkey\nattempts++ / maybe revoke]
    N -- Yes --> O[Passkey validated]

    J -- No --> O

    O --> P{Role = fieldServiceAgent?}
    P -- Yes --> Q[Load FieldServiceAgent profile by ID]
    Q --> R{Profile exists, unlinked,\nemail matches?}
    R -- No --> E8[400/404/409 Error\nProfile validation failed]
    R -- Yes --> S[Profile link allowed]
    P -- No --> T{Role = customer?}

    T -- Yes --> U[Load Customer profile by ID]
    U --> V{Profile exists, unlinked,\nemail matches?}
    V -- No --> E9[400/404/409 Error\nProfile validation failed]
    V -- Yes --> S
    T -- No --> S

    S --> W[Create User document\nUser.create(...)]
    W --> X{User creation success?}
    X -- No --> E10[400 Bad Request\nInvalid user data]
    X -- Yes --> Y[If linked profile exists:\nset profile.userAccount = user._id\nsave profile]

    Y --> Z{Passkey was used?}
    Z -- Yes --> AA[Update passkey status->consumed\nset consumedAt]
    Z -- No --> AB[Skip passkey update]

    AA --> AC[Generate JWT token]
    AB --> AC

    AC --> AD[201 Created response\nReturn user payload + token]

    subgraph DB[MongoDB Collections]
      DB1[(User)]
      DB2[(OnboardingPasskey)]
      DB3[(FieldServiceAgent)]
      DB4[(Customer)]
    end

    H --> DB1
    K --> DB2
    Q --> DB3
    U --> DB4
    W --> DB1
    Y --> DB3
    Y --> DB4
    AA --> DB2